529
00:34:16,740 --> 00:34:18,360
Oh come on, work with me.

530
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:20,680
We'll be hanging around
fixing carburetors,

531
00:34:20,780 --> 00:34:22,520
singing along with Drexel.

532
