00:51:46,940 --> 00:51:49,000
in a dogfight with Jordanian jets.

763
00:51:49,100 --> 00:51:51,800
Three Syrian MiGs attacked
the city of Magneto.

764
00:51:51,900 --> 00:51:53,160
In other news...

765
00:51:53,260 --> 00:51:55,800
What does that have to do

766
00:51:55,900 --> 00:52:00,280
with the Christian church
in the state of Tennessee?

767
00:52:00,380 --> 00:52:02,160
Everything!

768
00:52:02,260 --> 00:52:05,921
It has to do with everything!

769
00:52:07,100 --> 00:52:10,920
We are commanded by the word of God,

770
00:52:11,020 --> 00:52:14,920
to give him no rest from our prayers.

771
00:52:15,020 --> 00:52:19,921
For who? Today, for Israel.

772
00:52:21,740 --> 00:52:24,760
Our precious Lord and savior

773
00:52:24,860 --> 00:52:27,804
was himself a Jew!

774
00:52:29,620 --> 00:52:31,760
If we love God,

775
00:52:31,860 --> 00:52:35,240
we must love what God loves.

776
00:52:35,340 --> 00:52:38,280
And God loves his chosen people!

777
00:52:40,820 --> 00:52:44,200
I've symbolically lit

778
00:52:44,300 --> 00:52:47,480
the eight candles of
the Hanukkah menorah.

779
00:52:47,580 --> 00:52:53,722
God's people need that
Hanukkah miracle again.

780
00:52:57,500 --> 00:53:01,640
Israel won the war.
A modern day miracle.

781
00:53:01,740 --> 00:53:04,960
But our miracle,
to have a family of our own,

782
00:53:05,060 --> 00:53:07,680
apparently wasn't meant to be.

783
00:53:07,780 --> 00:53:10,680
The doctors said Ryan
and I would never have

784
00:53:10,780 --> 00:53:13,042
one of these precious gifts.

785
00:53:18,940 --> 00:53:21,760
He just seems so directionless.

786
00:53:21,860 --> 00:53:24,680
He needs something beyond
just making a living.

787
00:53:24,780 --> 00:53:26,440
A calling perhaps?

788
00:53:26,540 --> 00:53:28,680
It's time.

789
00:53:28,780 --> 00:53:31,000
It's time to tell him the truth.

790
00:53:31,100 --> 00:53:36,000
Every night, I see that man's face,

791
00:53:36,100 --> 00:53:39,680
making me give my word

792
00:53:39,780 --> 00:53:41,720
not to say anything

793
00:53:41,820 --> 00:53:44,969
until they're both gone.

794
00:53:46,660 --> 00:53:51,080
It's been a thorn in my
side for 31 years, mother.

795
00:53:51,180 --> 00:53:55,080
I think about it.
Every day.

