Whoo!

1108
01:14:09,020 --> 01:14:12,920
We believe City Lights is a smash hit.

1109
01:14:18,300 --> 01:14:20,200
Now, Ryan,

1110
01:14:20,300 --> 01:14:23,006
I want you to hear me, brother.

1111
