Oh, it's so good to have you kids here.

1143
01:17:15,020 --> 01:17:18,000
That is the sweetest dress on you.

1144
01:17:18,100 --> 01:17:19,200
Why, thank you.

1145
01:17:19,300 --> 01:17:21,880
And, honey, you look better.

1146
01:17:21,980 --> 01:17:23,440
Thank you, Mama.

1147
01:17:23,540 --> 01:17:25,480
Are you back work yet?

1148
01:17:25,580 --> 01:17:28,360
Not yet, Mama.
Not yet.

1149
01:17:28,460 --> 01:17:31,040
Brother Wade, what's new at church?

1150
01:17:31,140 --> 01:17:35,120
Not much, really.

1151
01:17:35,220 --> 01:17:39,211
Except the board asked
me to resign on Monday.

1152
01:17:45,820 --> 01:17:48,280
Forty years.

1153
