Forty years.
Practically built that place

1154
01:17:50,780 --> 01:17:51,840
with my own two hands.

1155
01:17:51,940 --> 01:17:55,360
He used to go in his short
pants and start the coal fire

1156
01:17:55,460 --> 01:17:58,080
at five o'clock in the
morning before worship.

1157
01:17:58,180 --> 01:18:00,200
That's right.

1158
