1297
01:27:41,820 --> 01:27:45,120
I never been small,
I've always been tall

1298
01:27:45,220 --> 01:27:47,760
I got a great, big love for you

1299
01:27:47,860 --> 01:27:50,600
Yeah, yeah, yeah, baby

1300
01:27:50,700 --> 01:27:52,360
Come on now!

1301
01:27:54,500 --> 01:27:56,409
Give it to me

1302
01:28:06,660 --> 01:28:11,243
Oh, the hands are tied

1303
01:28:15,060 --> 01:28:20,963
Oh, I cannot see what's
right in front of me

1304
01:28:23,820 --> 01:28:28,280
Where in the world will I
be with my next step I take

1305
01:28:28,380 --> 01:28:31,280
Time, it keeps playing its tricks on me

1306
01:28:31,380 --> 01:28:35,560
As I move along, feel me get closer

1307
01:28:35,660 --> 01:28:39,560
'Cause I know this there's
something about ya

1308
01:28:41,340 --> 01:28:44,080
I can take a trip to see
all there is to see

1309
01:28:44,180 --> 01:28:47,840
I can be in jail then set free

1310
01:28:47,940 --> 01:28:52,240
Getting trashed by a queen,
laid out at her feet

1311
01:28:52,340 --> 01:28:56,604
But in the end,
there's something about ya

1312
01:29:49,540 --> 01:29:51,360
I'm sorry, baby.

1313
01:29:51,460 --> 01:29:56,320
I just thought it was some
kind of answer to prayer.

1314
01:29:56,420 --> 01:29:57,560
We'll figure something out.

1315
01:29:57,660 --> 01:29:59,171
Okay?

1316
01:30:02,740 --> 01:30:07,402
